                'description' => '<p>Code barcode readers feature lithium-ion batteries. The batteries are long-life, allowing readers to be used for more than a complete shift at the highest use rate. Code’s modular design allows a user to quickly exchange a drained battery with a charged battery without taking a barcode reader out-of-service.</p>',
