            104 => 
            array (
                'id' => 105,
                'name' => 'Mobile Enterprise SDK',
            'description' => '<p>The <i><strong>Mobile Enterprise</strong></i> software SDK utilizes the industry-leading CortexDecoder barcode reading technology, featuring over 40 decoding algorithms and industry-leading read rates. Mobile Enterprise excels for applications built for mobile devices used within business enterprises for internal use. Mobilize your scanning, mobilize your enterprise. CortexDecoder Mobile Enterprise has:</p><ul><li><strong>Market-defining read performance on 1D, 2D, postal, and direct part mark barcodes</strong></li><li><strong>Reliable scanning of crumpled, smudged, ripped, scathed, improperly printed, and other barcodes in poor conditions</strong></li><li><strong>Built-in barcode reading proficiency from the harshest applications and environments</strong></li></ul><p>CortexDecoder Mobile Enterprise not only enables smartphones like the Apple iPhone and Samsung Galaxy to read barcodes like a purpose-built barcode reader, but it also features productivity add-ons that can take your applications further, like:</p><ul><li><strong>Identification parsing for age verification and rapid form entry</strong></li><li><strong>GS1 and UDI parsing support for healthcare applications</strong></li><li><strong>Simultaneous multiple barcode reading for enhanced productivity</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Best Barcode Scanning Solution</strong></p><p>Zero-miss barcode scanning on any platform. Every scan – every time.</p><p>CortexDecoder Mobile software delivers persistent decoding excellence on any platform. The changing technology landscape has shaped a new kind of customer–turn any mobile device with an embedded camera into a true enterprise-grade barcode reader.</p><figure class="image"><img src="/storage/186/image.png"></figure><p>The platform solutions you need.</p><ul><li>Android Barcode Scanning Software</li><li>Linux Barcode Scanning Software</li><li>Apple Barcode Scanning Software</li><li>Windows Barcode Scanning Software</li><li>Xamarin SDK Barcode Scanning API</li></ul><p><i>If a mobile SDK isn’t right for your project, check out our advanced CortexDecoder Embedded OEM software</i></p><h4>&nbsp;Technical Specifications:</h4><p><strong>&nbsp;Minimum Recommended Image Resolution:&nbsp;</strong></p><ul><li>1 megapixel</li></ul><p><strong>Barcode Symbologies Supported:&nbsp;</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Direct Part Marks</strong>: Barcodes applied by laser or chemical etching, or inkjet printed. Will also read Data Matrix marks that have been dot peened to a surface.</li><li><strong>1D</strong>:<ul><li>Codabar</li><li>Code 11</li><li>Code 32</li><li>Code 39</li><li>Code 93</li><li>Code 128</li><li>IATA 2 of 5</li><li>Interleaved 2 of 5</li><li>GS1 DataBar (RSS)</li><li>Hong Kong 2 of 5</li><li>Matrix 2 of 5</li><li>MSI Plessey</li><li>NEC 2 of 5</li><li>Plessey</li><li>Straight 2 of 5</li><li>Telepen</li><li>Trioptic</li><li>UPC/EAN/JAN</li><li>IATA 2 of 5</li><li>NEC 2 of 5</li><li>BC412</li><li>Pharmacode</li></ul></li><li><strong>Stacked</strong>:<ul><li>GS1 Composite (CC-A/CC-B/CC-C)</li><li>MicroPDF417</li><li>PDF417</li><li>Code 49</li><li>Codablock F</li></ul></li><li><strong>2D</strong>:<ul><li>Aztec Code</li><li>Code 49</li><li>Codablock F</li><li>Data Matrix</li><li>Han Xin</li><li>MaxiCode</li><li>MicroQR</li><li>QR Code</li><li>QR Code Model 1</li><li>Dot Code</li><li>Grid Matrix</li><li>GS1 DataBar</li></ul></li><li><strong>Postal Codes</strong>:<ul><li>USPS Postnet</li><li>USPS Planet</li><li>Australian Post</li><li>USPS Intelligent Mail</li><li>Japan Post</li><li>KIX Code</li><li>UK Royal Mail</li><li>Dutch Post</li><li>Korea Post</li><li>Canada Post</li><li>UPI ID-tags</li></ul></li><li><strong>Proprietary 2D</strong>:<ul><li>GoCode® (Additional License Required)</li></ul></li><li><strong>E-LEVEL 1 Reads</strong>:<ul><li>Codabar</li><li>Code 39</li><li>Code 93</li><li>Code 128</li><li>Interleaved 2 of 5</li><li>GS1 DataBar (RSS)</li><li>UPC/EAN/JAN</li><li>PDF417</li><li>QR Code</li></ul></li><li><strong>E-LEVEL 2 Reads</strong>:<ul><li>All 1D and 2D Symbologies, Postal Codes, and Stacked Codes</li></ul></li></ul><p>&nbsp;<strong>O/S Support</strong>:&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Android 4.4 and higher</li><li>iOS 8 and higher</li><li>Windows 10 Mobile</li></ul>',
                'short' => '<p>This software package was built for high-speed, zero-miss barcode reading from any mobile device with an embedded camera. It features flawless performance on the most demanding barcodes, in the most demanding environments. With this level of performance, you can now realistically consider consumer-grade mobile devices as true enterprise-grade barcode scanners. The Mobile Enterprise software developers kit has flexible licensing and integration support by Code Professional Services.</p>',
