            106 => 
            array (
                'id' => 107,
                'name' => 'Embedded SDK',
            'description' => '<p>The innovative and powerful decoding platform – <i><strong>CortexDecoder</strong></i> – was developed by experts with decades of experience delivering purpose-built barcode scanning solutions to OEMs, enterprise application developers, consumer apps, and fast-paced industries.&nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>The CortexDecoder SDK scanning algorithms have been leading the industry for over 20 years. A dedicated team of experts continue to deliver innovative development in data capture and barcode scanning solutions to developers worldwide, producing cutting-edge solutions in vision systems, edge computing, machine vision and an ever-expanding technology in industrial embedded applications.</p><h4>Features include:&nbsp;</h4><ul><li><strong>Zero-miss Reliability</strong> - Worldwide proven accuracy is a hallmark. CortexDecoder reads even the most complex barcodes; secure, dependable, reliable, and with enterprise-grade performance.</li><li><strong>Industry Leading Scan Rates</strong> - Read rates that are up to 6x faster than the competition – even when barcodes are damaged or distorted.</li><li><strong>Flexible OS Portability</strong> - A small footprint, optimized portability, and decades of experience make for easy integration to virtually any processing platform and operating system.</li><li><strong>Superior on Poor Quality Barcodes</strong> - Performance beyond the expected. Simply put, we just read barcodes others can’t. Fast, accurate, dependable.</li><li><strong>Most Support of Barcode Symbologies</strong> - Code CortexDecoder offers the most advanced bundle of decoding algorithms in the industry.</li><li><strong>Unrivaled Professional Support</strong> - Code Professional Services make SDK integration easy. Our engineers and experts work directly with your team for optimal results.</li><li><strong>Camera Flexibility</strong> - Our software supports numerous types of optics and cameras, providing you the flexibility to build your project as needed.</li></ul><p><i><strong>Simply the fastest and most innovative barcode scanning software available.</strong></i></p><p>Our experts are here to work with you through any embedded application. CortexDecoder software delivers persistent decoding excellence on any platform.&nbsp;</p><h4>Technical Specifications:&nbsp;</h4><p><strong>Minimum System Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>500 KB storage</li><li>500 KB RAM minimum, 1 MB RAM recommended</li><li>1 megapixel image resolution</li></ul><p><strong>O/S Support:</strong></p><ul><li>Software portability to any processing platform and OS – Android, iOS, Windows, Linux, custom, etc.</li></ul><p><strong>Symbologies Supported:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Direct Part Marks</strong>:<ul><li>DPM barcodes applied by laser or chemical etching, or inkjet print.</li><li>Will also read Data Matrix marks that have been dot peened to a surface.</li></ul></li><li><strong>1D</strong>:<ul><li>Codabar</li><li>Code 11</li><li>Code 32</li><li>Code 39</li><li>Code 93</li><li>Code 128</li><li>IATA 2 of 5</li><li>Interleaved 2 of 5</li><li>GS1 DataBar (RSS)</li><li>Hong Kong 2 of 5</li><li>Matrix 2 of 5</li><li>MSI Plessey</li><li>NEC 2 of 5</li><li>Plessey</li><li>Straight 2 of 5</li><li>Telepen, Trioptic</li><li>UPC/EAN/JAN</li><li>IATA 2 of 5</li><li>NEC 2 of 5</li><li>BC412</li><li>Pharmacode</li></ul></li><li><strong>Stacked</strong>:<ul><li>GS1 Composite (CC-A/CC-B/CC-C)</li><li>MicroPDF417</li><li>PDF417</li><li>Code 49</li><li>Codablock F</li></ul></li><li><strong>2D</strong>:<ul><li>Aztec Code</li><li>Code 49</li><li>Codablock F</li><li>Data Matrix</li><li>Han Xin</li><li>MaxiCode</li><li>MicroQR</li><li>QR Code</li><li>QR Code Model 1</li><li>Dot Code</li><li>Grid Matrix</li><li>GS1 DataBar</li></ul></li><li><strong>Postal Codes</strong>:<ul><li>USPS Postnet</li><li>USPS Planet</li><li>Australian Post</li><li>USPS Intelligent Mail</li><li>Japan Post</li><li>KIX Code</li><li>UK Royal Mail</li><li>Dutch Post</li><li>Korea Post</li><li>Canada Post</li><li>UPU ID-tags</li></ul></li><li><strong>Proprietary 2D</strong>:<ul><li>GoCode® (Additional License Required)</li></ul></li></ul><p>CortexDecoder Embedded also enables users to add functionality that enhances data output for a variety of applications. Below is a sample of enhancements we’ve helped engineer for our customers.</p><ul><li><strong>Identification parsing for age verification and rapid form entry</strong></li><li><strong>GS1 and UDI parsing support for healthcare applications</strong></li><li><strong>Simultaneous multiple barcode reading for enhanced productivity</strong></li></ul>',
                'short' => '<p><i><strong>CortexDecoder Embedded OEM</strong></i> SDK is for OEM device manufacturers looking to integrate the best, enterprise-grade barcode scanning functionality within the devices they produce. Whether your product is a purpose-built barcode reader, scan engine, kiosk, mobile computer, or any other device with a camera, CortexDecoder Embedded has been optimized for enterprise-grade performance to overcome the scanning challenges of barcode reading and data capture found throughout many industries. The CortexDecoder Embedded OEM software developers kit has flexible licensing and integration support by Code Professional Services.</p>',
